# The corpus data blob lives in the S3 corpus remote (content-addressed,
# add-only) and only the small `corpus.db.ref` pointer (written by
# `fedcourts corpus-push`) is committed to git. Never commit the blob itself,
# its download staging file, or its SQLite sidecar files.
/corpus.db
/corpus.db.partial
/corpus.db-wal
/corpus.db-shm
*.parquet
/index.db
